  "detailed_description": "<h1>Wishlist my roguelike city builder! :)</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><br>Regrowth is a puzzle game where you race against time to save islands from sinking.<br>Use plants and animals, collect and channel water... However, only with strategy and optimisation can you solve all the levels. <br>Will you be able to save the earthen realm?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346210/extras/51e8b589384e0896ece5a800998d96b4.poster.avif?t=1724997683\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346210/extras/51e8b589384e0896ece5a800998d96b4.webm?t=1724997683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346210/extras/51e8b589384e0896ece5a800998d96b4.mp4?t=1724997683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Watch out for ponds and rain because having water for your plants is crucial in these dry times!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346210/extras/f837af9de11ba10ba65c3076eb66d421.poster.avif?t=1724997683\" width=600 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346210/extras/f837af9de11ba10ba65c3076eb66d421.webm?t=1724997683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346210/extras/f837af9de11ba10ba65c3076eb66d421.mp4?t=1724997683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use different plants and tools, optimise your positioning and timing. Planting a plant at the wrong place could lose you the island!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346210/extras/7556c9d3f0211ab71efb243b229869ef.poster.avif?t=1724997683\" width=600 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346210/extras/7556c9d3f0211ab71efb243b229869ef.webm?t=1724997683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346210/extras/7556c9d3f0211ab71efb243b229869ef.mp4?t=1724997683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Time your decisions and manage your water supply well because the land dries, the time is limited, and the seasons change!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346210/extras/1d7fccf1c301aad37470eeba50c6299b.poster.avif?t=1724997683\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346210/extras/1d7fccf1c301aad37470eeba50c6299b.webm?t=1724997683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346210/extras/1d7fccf1c301aad37470eeba50c6299b.mp4?t=1724997683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346210/extras/d974e8b50998b7d89991af513f52f41f.poster.avif?t=1724997683\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346210/extras/d974e8b50998b7d89991af513f52f41f.webm?t=1724997683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346210/extras/d974e8b50998b7d89991af513f52f41f.mp4?t=1724997683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<br>Regrowth is a puzzle game where you race against time to save islands from sinking.<br>Use plants and animals, collect and channel water... However, only with strategy and optimisation can you solve all the levels. <br>Will you be able to save the earthen realm?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346210/extras/51e8b589384e0896ece5a800998d96b4.poster.avif?t=1724997683\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346210/extras/51e8b589384e0896ece5a800998d96b4.webm?t=1724997683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346210/extras/51e8b589384e0896ece5a800998d96b4.mp4?t=1724997683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Watch out for ponds and rain because having water for your plants is crucial in these dry times!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346210/extras/f837af9de11ba10ba65c3076eb66d421.poster.avif?t=1724997683\" width=600 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346210/extras/f837af9de11ba10ba65c3076eb66d421.webm?t=1724997683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346210/extras/f837af9de11ba10ba65c3076eb66d421.mp4?t=1724997683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use different plants and tools, optimise your positioning and timing. Planting a plant at the wrong place could lose you the island!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346210/extras/7556c9d3f0211ab71efb243b229869ef.poster.avif?t=1724997683\" width=600 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346210/extras/7556c9d3f0211ab71efb243b229869ef.webm?t=1724997683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346210/extras/7556c9d3f0211ab71efb243b229869ef.mp4?t=1724997683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Time your decisions and manage your water supply well because the land dries, the time is limited, and the seasons change!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346210/extras/1d7fccf1c301aad37470eeba50c6299b.poster.avif?t=1724997683\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346210/extras/1d7fccf1c301aad37470eeba50c6299b.webm?t=1724997683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346210/extras/1d7fccf1c301aad37470eeba50c6299b.mp4?t=1724997683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346210/extras/d974e8b50998b7d89991af513f52f41f.poster.avif?t=1724997683\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346210/extras/d974e8b50998b7d89991af513f52f41f.webm?t=1724997683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1346210/extras/d974e8b50998b7d89991af513f52f41f.mp4?t=1724997683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
